\nAlexandra finishes the bottle of vodka. Everyone except Mailx is looking in her direction. Maybe he is too. \"I'm parched,\" she says. \"A girl really feels the lack of humidity out here on the Jovian moons,\" she says as Finnian's eyes light up and he gestures in laughter towards the Captain. I look around for something to clean the spill up with as I make myself another drink. We might be a million miles from where we meant to be and ten million miles from where we want to be but at least for the moment we're right where we belong. Together.
