\BIntroduction\b
\nIt is the future.\n
You are Ensign Ja'Rod Butler, returning from an extended shore leave, back on the spaceship known as the HMCS Plagoo.\n
Two minutes ago, you were alerted to the fact that a werewolf has somehow gotten onto the ship. One minute ago you made it into the quarters of the Plagoo's Captain to wake her up.\n
With any luck you'll be able to get rid of the werewolf without it hurting anyone. But, spoiler, check your inventory.\n
You're not carrying any luck.
\n[Press a key...]
