\nEnceladus is written with Hugo, a powerful language capable of producing graphical text adventures for many different platforms. This game is currently supports the following operating systems directly:\n
Windows (7, 8, Vista, XP, 98, 10), Mac OS X, Linux (tested on Ubuntu, but should work on all).\n
